Welcome to color change app

Background color of tye screen can be changed by pressing the buttons.
Three options are provided:
- select a color by pressing the button from a fixed set of colors 
- select randon set of colors by pressing the button, each time pressing the button will chnage the color randomly.
- auto color change: press the button and the color will chnage automatic reandom colors every second. Press the same button again to stop the color switching.
